channel.title: My Goal
channel.description:
Well I got back into RuneScape about a month ago. I found out there is this new cape called the Completionist Cape, and I want one. I also found out that every single skill is a lot easier to train. In the past month I've gained 14m exp and gained 120 levels. In the past 4 days I've gained about 1m exp each. Here's the list that I started. If anyone wants to help me out that no longer plays RuneScape and give me some money for the more expensive skills, I would gladly appreciate it.
My name is Wonder r if you want to look me up and track my progress. :P I will take a picture of my skills once a week at Sunday.
List: [s]99 Defence[/s] [img]http://s11.postimage.org/6uv5k1flv/99defence.jpg[/img] 99 Ranged 99 Prayer 99 Magic 99 Runecrafting 99 Construction 99 Agility 99 Herblore 99 Thieving 99 Crafting 99 Fletching 99 Slayer 99 Hunter 99 Mining 99 Smithing 99 Fishing [s]99 Firemaking[/s] [img]http://s16.postimg.org/y3ty5ejl1/99firemaking2_17_13.jpg[/img] [s]99 Woodcutting[/s] [img]http://s11.postimg.org/v9xz3602b/99woodcutting61313.jpg[/img] 99 Farming 99 Summoning 120 Dungeoneering
